N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 630.8 - Target clientele

State Regulations

The target clientele of the center shall be displaced
homemakers, as defined in article 23-B of the Labor Law, and who are in their
middle years, 35-60. However, no person above or below such age group who is a
displaced homemaker shall be denied the center's services. Notes
